item.title: Prayer bpn12425 in Namibia
item.description: Hompa, Karunga wande! Ove mudongononi po ndjo, muyambeki vitapa, mutunditipo liguvo! Vyashiri, ame kuna kukushungida mukughupira po ndjo dauno ogho ana shuvo shidwata sharutu a kanduke mughudjuni wapampepo. Hompa wande! Va kushure kumaundjoni ghavo, tundita po liguvo lyavo, shinta likurundema lyavo mushite. Va renke va ngene mushipata shalirago, va kushure namema ghamakushuki ngudu, va pe ashi va kukeye shikoda shoye pandundu yayire. (Source category: Rugciriku : KUVAFE) (Bahaiprayers.net ID: 12425)

item.title: Prayer bpn12429 in Namibia
